  <h1>
   Date And Time
  </h1>
  <span>
   GameMaker
  </span>
  has a great many functions and variables related to getting the date and time and calculating other values based off of them. By default these functions return the
  <b>
   local
  </b>
  time as set by the system, but you can use the following function to switch between local and UTC time:
  <ul>
   <li>
    <a href="date_set_timezone.htm">
     date_set_timezone
    </a>
   </li>
   <li>
    <a href="date_get_timezone.htm">
     date_get_timezone
    </a>
   </li>
  </ul>
